snippet.title: Andhra King Taluka Trailer | Ram Pothineni | Upendra | Mahesh Babu P | Bhagyashri Borse
snippet.description:
Andhra King Taluka Trailer on Mythri Movie Makers.

Andhra King Taluka - A BIOPIC OF A FAN is an Upcoming 2025 Telugu Movie starring Ram Pothineni, Upendra and Bhagyashri Borse. The film is written and directed by Mahesh Babu P and produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers. Music is by Vivek & Mervin. 

In Cinemas from 27th November, 2025.

snippet.title: Kamaal Hai | King & Aditya Dev | Sahher Bambba | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
With ‚ÄúKamaal Hai,‚Äù King kicks off a brand new chapter in his musical journey. A pop-fuelled anthem 
brought to life alongside Aditya Dev, packed with swagger, charm, and signature King wit, it‚Äôs driven by infectious hooks, slick wordplay, an undeniable groove, and celebrates desire and confidence in equal measure. A larger-than-life declaration of love and self-assuredness, King blends his sharp lyricism with a sound that‚Äôs vibrant, global, and unmistakably him, marking the start of an exciting new era of his sonic showcase and energy. At its core, ‚ÄúKamaal Hai‚Äù is King at his most magnetic ‚Äî playful, poetic, and completely in control.

snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the enchanting melodies of Alka Yagnik, a voice that defined romance in the 2000s. This collection features the timeless gem "Ikrar Ho Na Jaye" from the movie Zinda Dil, a song that captures the tender emotions of love and longing. Alka Yagnik's voice is a vessel of heartfelt expressions, her renditions painting vivid tapestries of affection and passion. Her songs transport us to a world where love reigns supreme, and every note resonates with the purest emotions. 

Experience the magic of these unforgettable songs, each a testament to Alka Yagnik's unparalleled artistry. Let the music evoke cherished memories and stir the depths of your heart. Indulge in the sweet nostalgia of the 2000s and revel in the beauty of these timeless compositions.



Credits :

Album: Zinda Dil
Artist: Alka Yagnik

Shree Brar presents the Official Music Video of Banda Ik Marona. It is a powerful Punjabi song with a gangsta vibe and emotional feel. The track shows a man who has left his old crime life and is now living clean, but still shares his past and pain with the girl he loves.
With strong lyrics by Shree Brar and soulful vocals by Jasmeen Akhtar, this song brings attitude, emotion, and a catchy hook ‚Äî perfect for Punjabi music fans.
